sources.description: Season Salad - Salad-e fasl (2005) Synopsis Leila, a girl from a poor family, who has no choice but to pick pocket in order to make ends meet. Leila meets Hamid Doosdar, an investor Businessman, while riding Metro that changes her life direction. Leila falls in love with Hamid and there is only one thing on their way, Hamid's wife. About this movie Title: Season Salad - Salad-e fasl (2005) Directed by: Fereydoon Jeyrani Date of birth: 10 February 1951, Kashmar, Iran Writing credits: Fereydoon Jeyrani , Khosro Shakibai Music: Karen Homayunfar Year: 2005 Country: Iran Language: Farsi Color: Color Runtime: 90 min.
